  "contenu": [
    {
      "type": "texte",
      "value": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> une fonction définie sur\nun ensemble <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{D}\\)</span> de <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathbb{R}^2\\)</span>, à valeurs dans <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{R}\\)</span>. Soit <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(a\\in \\mathcal{D}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Dire si les affirmations suivantes sont vraies ou fausses. On ne\ndemande pas de justifier mais une mauvaise réponse entraîne une pénalité\nde points.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> admet des dérivées\npartielles en <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a\\)</span>, alors <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est différentiable en a.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>FAUX</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> admet des dérivée\npartielles en <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a\\)</span>, alors <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est continue en <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(a\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>VRAI</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est différentiable en tout\npoint de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{D}\\)</span>, alors <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est de classe <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(C^1\\)</span> sur <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{D}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>FAUX</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "<p>Si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Df(a)=0\\)</span>, alors <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> admet un extremum local en <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(a\\)</span>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "<p>FAUX</p>\n"
